# Ralph Tools Guide

Copy this file to your project as `RALPH_TOOLS.md` and customize it.

## Testing

- Unit tests: `npm test`
- E2E tests: `npm run test:e2e`
- Type checking: `npm run typecheck`
- Linting: `npm run lint`

## Browser Automation

You have access to Playwright MCP for browser automation. Use it for:
- E2E testing
- Visual verification
- Form interaction testing
- Screenshot comparisons

## Build

- Development: `npm run dev` (starts on port 3000)
- Production build: `npm run build`
- Preview build: `npm run preview`

## Project Structure

- `src/` - Source code
- `tests/` - Test files
- `public/` - Static assets

## Important Notes

- Always run tests before committing
- Follow existing code style
- Update types when changing interfaces
